        "## System of nonlinear equations\n",
        "\n",
        "* For example, consider the following system of two multivariate and nonlinear equations:\n",
        "\n",
        "  $$\n",
        "    \\begin{aligned}\n",
        "    y - x^3 -2x^2 +1 &= 0\\\\ \n",
        "    y + x^2 -1 &= 0 \n",
        "    \\end{aligned}\n",
        "  $$"
      ],
      "id": "228093a9"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "def f(x):\n",
        "  return [x[1] -x[0]**3 -2*x[0]**2 +1, x[1] +x[0]**2 -1]"
      ],
      "id": "a46be15d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "optimize.fsolve(f, [1, 1])"
      ],
      "id": "da8bff31",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "optimize.broyden1(f, [1, 1])"
      ],
      "id": "59486ca4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
